'''Timothy S. O'Brien''' was an author for [[Star Wars: The Roleplaying Game]] produced by [[West End Games]] (WEG). He got his start in [[1993]], when he learned that WEG was creating a new publication, the ''[[Star Wars Adventure Journal]]'', which was looking for new writers. His submission, "Rebel Privateers!," was published in the second issue of the ''Journal''.

O'Brien went on to write several sourcebooks for WEG, several of which revisited the [[Pirate/Legends|pirate]] theme of that first article.

